tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_id INT,
    content_id INT,
    collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
    collaboration_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE ContentCollaborations (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    collaboration_name VARCHAR(255),
    collaboration_description TEXT,
    partner_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (partner_id) REFERENCES Partners(partner_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Partners (
    partner_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_name VARCHAR(255),
    partnership_type VARCHAR(50),
    partnership_start_date DATE,
    partnership_end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
    partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_name VARCHAR(255),
    partner VARCHAR(255),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE sponsored_content (
    content_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    content_title VARCHAR(255),
    sponsor VARCHAR(255),
    publish_date DATE,
    content_type VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    collaboration_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    collaboration_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    partner_id UUID,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
);

CREATE TABLE content_collaborations (
    collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    collaboration_name VARCHAR(255),
    collaboration_description TEXT,
    collaboration_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE partners (
    partner_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_name VARCHAR(255),
    partner_type VARCHAR(50),
    partner_email VARCHAR(255),
    partner_phone VARCHAR(15)
)

CREATE TABLE sponsorships (
    sponsorship_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    sponsorship_description TEXT,
    sponsorship_date DATE,
    sponsorship_amount DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE collaboration_partners (
    collaboration_id INT,
    partner_id INT,
    partnership_date DATE,
    PRIMARY KEY (collaboration_id, partner_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (collaboration_id) REFERENCES content_collaborations(collaboration_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (partner_id) REFERENCES partners(partner_id)
)

CREATE TABLE sponsored_content (
    content_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    content_title VARCHAR(255),
    content_description TEXT,
    sponsorship_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (sponsorship_id) REFERENCES sponsorships(sponsorship_id)
)
